Package: notification-player
Version: 1.0.0
Section: sound
Priority: optional
Architecture: mips64el
Depends: alsa-utils | pulseaudio-utils, libc6 (>= 2.28)
Recommends: mpv | ffmpeg
Maintainer: Your Name <your.email@example.com>
Description: HTTP API remote audio notification player
 Notification Player is a lightweight service that provides HTTP API
 for remote audio notification playback. It's optimized for Loongson
 3A4000 MIPS64el architecture.
 .
 Features:
  * HTTP API for remote trigger
  * Multiple audio player support (aplay, paplay, mpv, ffplay)
  * Queue management
  * Volume control
  * Token authentication